                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="text-h5">2</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-bold"
                                    >Competitive Analysis & Market Research:</span
                                >
                                I study how existing products address similar problems,
                                identifying opportunities for innovation and better
                                user experiences.
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="text-h5">3</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-bold"
                                    >User Journey Mapping:</span
                                >
                                I map out complete user flows to understand pain
                                points and opportunities for improvement throughout
                                the entire experience.
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
                <div id="design-panel" class="tab-panel hidden">
                    <ol class="process-steps">
                        <li>
                            <span class="text-h5">1</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-bold"
