                        <li>
                            <span class="text-h5">3</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-bold"
                                    >User Testing & Iteration:</span
                                >
                                I conduct usability tests with real users, gather
                                feedback, and rapidly iterate on the design based
                                on observed behavior.
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="text-h5">4</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-bold"
                                    >Design System Development:</span
                                >
                                I create reusable components and design patterns
                                that ensure consistency and accelerate future development.
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
                <div id="implementation-panel" class="tab-panel hidden">
                    <ol class="process-steps">
                        <li>
                            <span class="text-h5">1</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-bold"
                                    >Technical Architecture Planning:</span
                                >
                                I plan the technical implementation strategy, ensuring
                                the final product will be performant, accessible,
                                and maintainable.
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="text-h5">2</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-bold"
                                    >Frontend Implementation:</span
                                >
                                I build pixel-perfect, responsive interfaces using
