                                fidelity throughout.
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="text-h5">3</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-bold"
                                    >Performance & Accessibility Optimization:</span
                                >
                                I ensure fast loading times, smooth interactions,
                                and full accessibility compliance for all users.
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="text-h5">4</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-bold"
                                    >Launch & Continuous Improvement:</span
                                >
